window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>In a world where the AI Apocalypse has transformed life into a brutal game of survival, humanity's last hope lies in turning back the clock.</b></p> <p>Liam Bell, a seasoned warrior at the end of his rope, is given a second chance. With a unique class that may give him the edge he needs, he is determined to rewrite history and save the remnants of humanity.</p> <p>As Liam battles monstrous foes and navigates treacherous alliances, he must level up rapidly, from weak to strong, harnessing the evolving power of his bloodline. Every step forward brings new challenges, and the fate of humanity grows ever more precarious.</p> <p>Can Liam reach the mythical Level 100 and attain the power to create safe havens before the relentless onslaught of monsters and invading species overwhelms him?</p> <p>AI Apocalypse: Restart <i>is the thrilling first book in a LitRPG/GameLit series, promising a blend of progression, intense action, and relatable characters.</i></p> <p><i>Dive into</i> AI Apocalypse: Restart <i>and join Liam on his quest to turn the tide in a world where every decision could mean life or death. The numbers go up, but the stakes have never been higher!</i></p>"; 
